text: came here to get contact lenses and felt really odd trying them for the first time. but thanks to ms wendy's patience, I managed to put them in despite feeling nervous since I was afraid that I wld poke my own eyes. my contacts also managed to get delivered a few days bfr the actual date, so I was rly happy abt that. wld highly recommend coming here!!

I would like to express my gratitude to Mr William Tan, who always has patience to guide customers and is also very knowledgeable. He also go an extra mile to help customers. Highly Recommended!
